title: New England Patriots Super Bowl Parade ... Stickin' It to Goodell! (LIVE STREAM)
text:
New England Patriots Super Bowl Parade ... Stickin' It to Goodell! Patriots Super Bowl Parade Stickin' It to Goodell! (Live Stream) 1 2/7/2017 7:53 AM PST 
Here it is ... the moment everyone in New England has been waiting for -- Tom Brady parading the Vince Lombardi trophy down the streets of Boston! 
The Super Bowl victory parade is set to go down around 11 AM ET -- so stick around for that ... at the very least, it'll be interesting to see if the players take a few digs at Roger Goodell . 
Meanwhile in Atlanta ... sad.
